killing innocent animals?

323
00:19:23,596 --> 00:19:25,530
Hey, look, let's just
get one thing straight.

324
00:19:25,698 --> 00:19:27,265
I ain't maiming nothing.

325
00:19:27,433 --> 00:19:29,634
Whatever I see
and I aim at, I shoot.

326
00:19:29,802 --> 00:19:32,336
When I shoot it, I
kill it and then I eat it.

327
00:19:32,505 --> 00:19:33,982
So, you do kill those ducks?

328
00:19:34,006 --> 00:19:35,873
<i>Of course I do.
What am I gonna do,</i>

329
00:19:36,242 --> 00:19:37,719
cook 'em while they're
still moving around?

330
00:19:37,743 --> 00:19:39,277
That would be cruel.

331
00:19:39,445 --> 00:19:41,085
<i>That'd be bad.</i>

332
00:19:42,048 --> 00:19:44,460
So, this isn't an act? You're
actually proud of what you do?

333
00:19:44,484 --> 00:19:46,495
Of course I am. Why would
I do it if I'm not proud of it?

334
00:19:46,519 --> 00:19:47,996
And you go along with
everything he says?

335
00:19:48,020 --> 00:19:49,698
We've been married for 20 years.

336
00:19:49,722 --> 00:19:51,642
I don't go along with
everything he says,

337
00:19:51,724 --> 00:19:53,857
but on the things
that matter, yeah,

338
00:19:54,026 --> 00:19:55,959
I agree wholeheartedly.

339
00:19:56,329 --> 00:19:59,463
