to Jesus in every episode?

342
00:20:04,737 --> 00:20:07,338
Hey, we're not trying to
offend anybody, alright?

343
00:20:07,507 --> 00:20:09,985
<i>If they don't want to watch the
show, they can turn the channel.</i>

344
00:20:10,009 --> 00:20:11,609
As far as my praying to Jesus,

345
00:20:11,777 --> 00:20:14,912
my life and my whole
eternity belongs to God.

346
00:20:15,281 --> 00:20:19,817
All this stuff is temporary:
the money, fame, success.

347
00:20:19,985 --> 00:20:21,519
Temporary.

348
00:20:21,688 --> 00:20:23,254
Even life is temporary.

349
00:20:23,423 --> 00:20:25,223
Jesus, that's eternal.

350
00:20:25,391 --> 00:20:26,724
Jesus said this:

351
00:20:26,892 --> 00:20:28,826
<i>"Whoever acknowledges
me before men,"</i>

352
00:20:28,994 --> 00:20:31,662
he will acknowledge
before the Father in heaven.

353
00:20:31,831 --> 00:20:35,499
<i>"Whoever disowns me, I'll
disown him to the Father."</i>

354
00:20:35,668 --> 00:20:38,336
Now, those words are written
in red so they're important.

355
00:20:38,504 --> 00:20:39,837
And that's it?

356
00:20:40,005 --> 00:20:41,565
That's it. That's
what we're going with.

357
00:20:41,708 --> 00:20:43,241
Pretty simple, isn't it?

358
00:20:43,409 --> 00:20:44,742
Thanks for your time.

359
00:20:44,910 --> 00:20:46,470
Come on, let's go do
some acknowledging.

