00:20:46,613 --> 00:20:47,945
You're welcome to join us.

361
00:20:48,314 --> 00:20:50,581
<i>No thanks, I'm good.</i>

362
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:52,283
You're good?

363
00:20:52,452 --> 00:20:53,784
Alright.

