807
00:49:03,074 --> 00:49:04,473
Martin, right?

808
00:49:04,642 --> 00:49:07,944
Correct, and you're Mr. Josh.

809
00:49:08,112 --> 00:49:09,478
Yeah.

810
00:49:09,647 --> 00:49:14,016
Yeah, that's me, Mr. Josh.

811
00:49:14,185 --> 00:49:15,684
Hey, is that on
our reading list?

812
00:49:16,587 --> 00:49:18,287
No.

813
00:49:21,459 --> 00:49:25,227
Can I ask you a question?

814
00:49:25,396 --> 00:49:28,097
Yeah, sure.

815
00:49:28,266 --> 00:49:33,202
Why are you doing
what you are doing?

816
00:49:35,506 --> 00:49:37,451
