971
00:57:45,796 --> 00:57:49,465
<i>This is more of a merlot.</i>

972
00:57:49,633 --> 00:57:51,533
<i>You know, lying's not good.</i>

973
00:57:51,702 --> 00:57:54,470
<i>Lying to an ordained
minister is flat-out bad.</i>

974
00:57:54,638 --> 00:57:55,971
You know that, right?

975
00:57:57,541 --> 00:57:58,819
<i>Sir, I assure you this is
a different automobile.</i>

976
00:57:58,843 --> 00:58:01,209
<i>Here, try it out.</i>

977
00:58:04,748 --> 00:58:06,147
How'd your audition go?

978
00:58:06,316 --> 00:58:07,850
Oh, pretty good.

